{
  "stem": "11000.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they used to sing these anti-Semitic songs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember one very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It said, when the Jewish blood spatters from our knives, that's when life will get better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember my parents standing behind the curtains and watching who the people were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And every time it happened, they said, I can't believe that this one is also a member now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I can't believe that this person joined the party, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they must have become very depressed to see people that they had grew up with an associated with all of a sudden making such a turn.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then of course, the boycotting started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They erected signs that they shouldn't patronize and buy at Jewish establishments, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it started to affect our business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I remember they posted a Nazi photographer in front of our business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And his job was to take pictures, to keep a record of who the people were that still were buying in Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all in all, with the whole package, my dad felt that it wasn't too good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he couldn't see any way that it would get better for the time being.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he decided to move across the border, which we lived very close to the Dutch border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Linnich is very close, just a few miles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he did have business connections with people in Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it wasn't a big thing for us to just move the business over to the Dutch side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, in the Jewish community it was quite an upset.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were the first ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody ever heard of anybody leaving this town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they kind of were upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I asked them, what are you afraid of?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Are you chicken?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
